OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FStephen Fry wants King's   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FGuards to ditch bear fur   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Stephen Fry has called for an end to   
OL,6, the use of real fur in the bearskin    
OL,7, caps worn by the King's Guard on duties
OL,8, such as guarding Buckingham Palace.    
OL,10,FThe actor has backed an animal welfare 
OL,11,Fcampaign calling for fake fur to be    
OL,12,Fused rather than real bear fur.        
OL,14,F"Tradition is never an excuse for      
OL,15,Fcruelty," says Mr Fry, who is narrating
OL,16,Fa video which shows undercover film of 
OL,17,Fhow black bears are killed.            
OL,19,FThe Ministry of Defence says the bear  
OL,20,Ffur is from "legal and licensed hunts".
